azoy, un fun di andere zayt hot men gezogt di mentshn forn keyn AUSCHWITZ.

00:23:22.341 --> 00:23:24.750
un, un, un s'iz gevezn

00:23:24.750 --> 00:23:27.802
m'iz gevezn oyf di zayt vos m'hot nisht geshikt.

00:23:28.247 --> 00:23:32.375
ober shpeter hot men undz avekgenumen in GURS.

00:23:33.428 --> 00:23:36.937
GURS iz gevezn a bisl laykhter. azoy hot gezogt di mame.

00:23:36.937 --> 00:23:41.097
zi hot gefilt mer shoyn UNK, gegat fun di royte KREUTZ

00:23:41.146 --> 00:23:43.486
hobn zey shoyn gebrengt far kinder

00:23:43.486 --> 00:23:45.780
epes UNK tsu esn mit ales

00:23:45.780 --> 00:23:48.410
ober ikh derman mikh, ikh bin gevezn oyf a bet

00:23:48.410 --> 00:23:50.688
un s'iz gevezn oybn azoy

00:23:50.688 --> 00:23:52.642
azoy vi unter a dakh,

00:23:52.648 --> 00:23:56.371
s'iz nisht gevezn glaykh. s'iz gevezn UNK azelekhene

00:23:56.496 --> 00:23:59.193
un s'iz gevezn di ACHBARIM

00:23:59.193 --> 00:24:00.163
vos zenen

00:24:00.163 --> 00:24:01.673
adurkhgelofn

00:24:01.673 --> 00:24:04.449
un ikh hob azoy moyre biz haynt

00:24:04.449 --> 00:24:07.159
fun yede zakh vos krikht, fun a zhuk

00:24:07.199 --> 00:24:09.199
ikh ver meshuge, yede zakh.

00:24:09.199 --> 00:24:10.879
hob ikh genumen di laylekh

00:24:10.879 --> 00:24:14.363
un ikh hob mir gedekt di kop. ikh hob gezogt "ikh vil nisht zen."

00:24:14.363 --> 00:24:17.780
vayl, vayl s'iz nisht UNK moyre

00:24:17.780 --> 00:24:19.710
un m'hot nisht gegat keyn breyre.

00:24:20.307 --> 00:24:24.874
un m'hot gelozt di kinder in eyn zayt un di eltern fun di andere zayt.

00:24:24.998 --> 00:24:27.627
un in GURS iz men shoyn gevezn

00:24:27.627 --> 00:24:34.259
a bisl in a besere tsushtand. azoy hot gezogt di mame. ikh ken nisht makhn keyn untershid

00:24:34.259 --> 00:24:35.837
vayl s'iz nisht klor

00:24:35.837 --> 00:24:38.103
in mayn kop vos iz dort gevezn.

00:24:38.802 --> 00:24:40.267
un eyn mol

00:24:40.267 --> 00:24:43.200
iz gekumen a mentsh fun LYON

00:24:44.100 --> 00:24:46.518
iz men gevezn shoyn oyf di

00:24:46.518 --> 00:24:50.304
fraye plats. dos vos ikh hob gevolt zogn oykhet

00:24:50.378 --> 00:24:52.026
az

00:24:52.521 --> 00:24:54.222
adurkhgeyendik

00:24:54.222 --> 00:24:59.276
d- koydem kol ven m'iz geganen, dos iz nisht in gantsn azoy khronologish

00:24:59.276 --> 00:25:02.263
ober befor m'iz ongekumen in di CAMP

00:25:02.263 --> 00:25:03.891
un m'iz geganen in PAU

00:25:03.891 --> 00:25:07.924
ven m'iz adurkhgeganen di, di LIGNE DE DEMARCATION

00:25:07.924 --> 00:25:09.406
iz gevezn

00:25:09.480 --> 00:25:12.866
zeyer, zeyer aparat.

00:25:13.024 --> 00:25:14.463
vayl dort

00:25:14.463 --> 00:25:17.079
tomer m'hot getrofn oyf di veg

00:25:17.079 --> 00:25:18.300
a mentsh

00:25:18.424 --> 00:25:21.137
iz glaykh iz er gevezn farnumen.

00:25:21.137 --> 00:25:23.583
un s'hot nokh gebroykht di daytshn

00:25:23.583 --> 00:25:26.783
hobn nokh dort gebroykht tsu kenen adurkhgeyn

00:25:26.783 --> 00:25:28.463
mit di vogn.

00:25:29.173 --> 00:25:34.820
un m'iz geganen, m'iz, m'iz adurkhgeganen velder un felder un ales

00:25:34.820 --> 00:25:37.450
biz m'iz ongekumen oyf a plats

00:25:37.450 --> 00:25:39.720
vos zey zenen gevezn mit di MADRICH

00:25:39.720 --> 00:25:42.760
tsuzamen, un dort hot men undz gelozt shlofn.

00:25:43.112 --> 00:25:45.958
m'hot undz gelozt shlofn

00:25:46.437 --> 00:25:51.124
un ven m'iz dort ongekumen, biz m'iz dort ongekumen, hot men d- gebroykht

00:25:51.124 --> 00:25:52.947
adurkhtsugeyn a vaser.

00:25:52.947 --> 00:25:56.103
un far di vaser iz gevezn aza f-

00:25:56.103 --> 00:25:58.057
fald, aza feld

00:25:58.182 --> 00:26:00.524
un dos iz geganen shines

00:26:00.524 --> 00:26:01.787
fun a tsug.

00:26:02.620 --> 00:26:06.681
un dort iz gevezn daytshn vos zey hobn dos gehit.

00:26:06.737 --> 00:26:09.374
un der MADRICH hot gezogt tsvishn

00:26:09.374 --> 00:26:10.561
tsvey

00:26:10.602 --> 00:26:17.433
di tsvey zakhn, di, vi azoy ken men zogn? a grupe fun di mentshn

00:26:17.433 --> 00:26:19.846
eyner toysht zikh di tsveyte

00:26:19.846 --> 00:26:22.977
iz do a gevise tsayt vos s'iz keyner nishto.

00:26:22.977 --> 00:26:24.757
damolst muzn mir adurkhgeyn.

00:26:24.757 --> 00:26:27.197
dos iz gevezn efsher tsen minut.

00:26:27.207 --> 00:26:29.887
un er hot gezogt "vart, vart, vart, vart."

00:26:29.887 --> 00:26:33.624
m'hot gezen di rey- di tsigaretn fun di vartns.

00:26:33.624 --> 00:26:34.729
"yetst

00:26:34.729 --> 00:26:36.380
GO. ⟨NA AGID⟩."

00:26:36.403 --> 00:26:37.750
un me geyt

00:26:37.750 --> 00:26:41.910
un me, un me geyt langzam, eyns nokhn andern mit alemen

00:26:41.910 --> 00:26:43.319
un PITOM

00:26:43.319 --> 00:26:45.015
ikh farlir mayn shukh

00:26:45.015 --> 00:26:46.559
in di ⟨gleyze⟩.

00:26:46.559 --> 00:26:50.331
arayngeleygt di fus, kleyne fus, in di ⟨gleyze⟩

00:26:50.331 --> 00:26:53.471
un ikh s- sh- m'hot nisht gemegt tsu redn. ikh ⟨shushke⟩

00:26:53.471 --> 00:26:56.191
MAMAN, kh'hob nisht mer mayn shukh."

00:26:56.191 --> 00:26:59.531
zi zogt "s'iz gornisht BERTHEle. m'vet dir koyfn andere shikh.

00:26:59.531 --> 00:27:00.581
kum shnel.

00:27:00.581 --> 00:27:02.925
s'iz nisht yetst di moment tsu vartn."

00:27:03.066 --> 00:27:03.966
un ikh

00:27:03.966 --> 00:27:05.155
derman mikh

00:27:05.155 --> 00:27:06.691
azoy vi yetst

00:27:06.691 --> 00:27:07.633
az

00:27:07.656 --> 00:27:10.596
kh'hob getrakht biz kh'hob shoyn bakumen di por shikh

00:27:10.596 --> 00:27:12.726
zi vet mir nisht koyfn azoy shnel.

00:27:12.726 --> 00:27:15.740
ikh ze dos ⟨klor⟩ in mayn gedank

00:27:15.740 --> 00:27:16.830
az s'iz

00:27:16.830 --> 00:27:19.140
vu vet men koyfn? s'iz nishto keyn, keyn

00:27:19.140 --> 00:27:20.980
keyn kleyt. s'iz gor nishto.

00:27:21.274 --> 00:27:22.579
ober

00:27:22.579 --> 00:27:25.350
zi hot mir, z- z- zi hot gezogt UNK

00:27:25.350 --> 00:27:28.090
"neyn, ikh gey nisht. ikh gey nisht."

00:27:28.090 --> 00:27:32.080
un di mame "BERTHele, ikh bet dikh. ikh vel dir koyfn tsvey dray"

00:27:32.080 --> 00:27:34.760
un azoy langzam, langzam mit di hent

00:27:35.300 --> 00:27:38.430
un a nes iz geshen. zi hot getrofn di shikh.

00:27:38.942 --> 00:27:42.119
hot men gekent, iz men aribergeganen

00:27:42.119 --> 00:27:44.271
un m'hot gekent geyn vayter

00:27:44.271 --> 00:27:45.061
un

00:27:45.152 --> 00:27:47.596
s'iz adurkhgeganen besholem.
